item.description:
For more details see:  ayarncrawl.com 

There are four dates on the calendar.  Carrie volunteers to host/drive on the two most popular.  Are there any other driver/hosts available? 

We'll plan to meet early enough to be at the first shop at opening and hit as many as we can before we need to be back home.
item.why: "North Shore Boston is a treasure trove of yarn shops. Each shop has its own personality and offerings. We're really looking forward to celebrating the colorful creativity north of Boston with all of you! Hope you can join us for the crawl."
item.name: North Shore Yarn Crawl
